18 ToTaL SiGnS oF fLiRtInG*-*-*-

*~*Guys*~*

1. She makes eye contact and smiles at you.

2. She hits you softly on the arm and laughs when you say something funny.

3. She flips her hair when she's talking to you.

4. She touches your arm when she talks to you.

5. She says, "No, I'm not telling you who I like!" with a big smile on her face

6. She asks you who you like or who you would go out with seemingly interested.

7. When you go to the movies with a bunch of your friends and she is almost always next to you.

8. She lets you play with her expensive jewelry.

9. She criticizes you on a girl you like.

10. You catch her staring at you.

11. She plays with your hair or tries to put make up on you.

12. Her friends outside of school and in school know about you, and says she talks about you a lot.

13. She knows your phone number and address.

14. She will try and talk, and spend time with you as much as possible

15. She instant messages you online 2 minutes after she signs on or she comes back from "away" when you come on.

16. She talks to your friends about you to make sure you like her.

17. She leaves you messages on your phone that just say "hi. wanted to know what you were doing."

18. You can tell shes smiling while you talk to her on the phone.



*~*Girls*~*

1. He stares at you a lot.

2. He hits you a lot. (just play hitting )

3. He uses the first thing that pops into his head to start a
conversation with you

4. He yelled, "Hi!", to your mom that day she picked you up from
school.

5. He blew off his buds to go see "Run Away Bride" with you cuz you couldn't get another girl pal to go and didn't want to go alone.

6. He tries to make you laugh anyway even if he gets hurt in the
process

7. Taking walks with him while hes with his friends becomes a routine.

8. His voice gets softer ("Hey, you") when ever you two talk.

9. You hung up on him. He called you back.

10. You where invited by him to a group outing.

11. He called you to talk about nothing at all.

12. He imitates your laugh. OK, you do snort sometimes. Which makes you laugh even harder.

13. He remembers little things you mention in casual conversation.

14. He sometimes stares straight into your eyes.

15. He finds every possible way to touch you (your hair, face, butt, thighs, ect.)

16. He asks to look in your purse.

17. He gets really close to you when he talks.

18. He tells your friends things he thinks about you...knowing that they will tell you.
